about.summary: The official Citation Style Language (CSL) styles and locale files.

name: rb-csl-styles
raw_recipe:
{% set name = "csl-styles" %}
{% set version = "1.0.1.9" %}

package:
  name: rb-{{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://rubygems.org/downloads/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.gem
  sha256: 5899db4404ef96e6d836ad2970f82c2c7e960dd6aa00e3feb58daff01720e882

build:
  noarch: generic
  number: 0
  script:
    - gem install -N -l -V --norc --ignore-dependencies {{ name }}-{{ version }}.gem
    - gem unpack {{ name }}-{{ version }}.gem
  skip: {{ win }}

requirements:
  host:
    - ruby
  run:
    - ruby
    - rb-csl >=1.0,<2

test:
  commands:
    - ruby -r {{ name|replace('-','/') }} -e 'exit 0'

about:
  home: https://rubygems.org/gems/{{ name }}
  license: CC-BY-SA-3.0
  summary: The official Citation Style Language (CSL) styles and locale files.

  doc_url: https://www.rubydoc.info/gems/{{ name }}
  dev_url: https://github.com/inukshuk/{{ name }}

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - sodre
